{"tid":1741963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日再聽喊到10點帶領喊口號既人喊⋯⋯","createTime":"2019-11-20T14:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T14:45:12.000Z","uid":112551,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"acde791d59cce32df65bffe8f8c7f1fd30da03ed","tid":1741963,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:35:32.000Z","msg":"我唔識個人係邊個，但理大事件發生前個人仲會響窗邊大喊，風雨不改，<br />\n但過理大事件過咗幾日，再聽唔到佢帶領大家10點喊口號 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />⋯<br />\n唔知發生咩事，我相信人既相念唔會一瞬即閃，人慢慢減少，願意拋頭露面的人慢慢被捉晒。<br />\n我以前仲笑9政府，捉2000人你捉得晒？家陣再捉5000人，雖然我相信好多人都未必可以被控，但身邊既人因為公義而消失，我覺得好心寒。<br />\n我相信歷史會為佢地還一個公道。"},{"pid":"0303ee658bb25f2d6137b25e44713bc431471243","tid":1741963,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:41:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac0ade75d0fa030bb0a430f9a853c9bac298d9f","tid":1741963,"uid":176121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望佢係平安"},{"pid":"f85f153215a23821a199c1fc85c5f95e49d9a951","tid":1741963,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:42:40.000Z","msg":"借過位<br />\n[多圖]11.21 曙光行動2.0，721 4.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1741920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1741920</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"765c3248094cb58a3f5738d433fb4dc536aa955e","tid":1741963,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:43:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>一齊入嚟睇致勝關鍵！！！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[拒絕分化！]古人一早教我地點贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1739422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.k